.npmjs.com/package/eslint-plugin-paths\n\n### Topics\n\ntypescript eslint eslint-plugin build-tools codeanalysis tsconfig\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nApache-2.0 license\n\nActivity\n\n### Stars\n\n2 stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n2 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n0 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Contributors 2\n\n  * vitonsky Robert Vitonsky\n  * dependabot[bot]\n\n## Languages\n\n  * TypeScript 77.4%\n  * JavaScript 19.4%\n  * Shell 3.2%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
